---
---
<section class="fcta" id="quote">
  <img class="fcta__bg" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503389152951-9c3d8d9f8c09?w=1400&q=80&fit=crop&crop=center" alt="A Plumber Happy Valley team member ready to book a service in Happy Valley" loading="lazy" />
  <div class="fcta__texture" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="fcta__inner wrap reveal">
    <span class="fcta__eyebrow">Ready When You Are</span>
    <h2>Book a licensed Happy Valley plumber today.</h2>
    <p>Fixed upfront pricing, lifetime labour warranty, and $50 off your first service. Call now or request a free quote and we'll get straight back to you.</p>
    <div class="fcta__btns">
      <a class="btn btn--primary" href="tel:0880000000">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6.6 10.8a15 15 0 0 0 6.6 6.6l2.2-2.2a1 1 0 0 1 1-.24 11.4 11.4 0 0 0 3.6.58 1 1 0 0 1 1 1V20a1 1 0 0 1-1 1A17 17 0 0 1 3 4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3.5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1 11.4 11.4 0 0 0 .58 3.6 1 1 0 0 1-.24 1Z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
        Call (08) 8000 0000
      </a>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="tel:0880000000">Request a Free Quote</a>
    </div>
    <span class="fcta__sub">$50 off your first service &middot; Lic. #333997</span>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .fcta { position: relative; background: var(--color-brand-secondary); overflow: hidden; }
  .fcta__bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; z-index: 0; opacity: .15; }
  .fcta__texture {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; opacity: .04; z-index: 1;
    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #fff 0, #fff 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 11px);
  }
  .fcta__inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin-inline: auto; padding-top: clamp(64px,8vw,100px); padding-bottom: clamp(64px,8vw,100px); }
  .fcta__eyebrow { display: inline-block; font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .16em; font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-brand-accent); margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .fcta__inner h2 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -.03em; font-size: clamp(28px,3.6vw,46px); line-height: 1.08; color: #fff; margin: 0 0 16px; }
  .fcta__inner p { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65; color: rgba(255,255,255,.78); margin: 0 auto 28px; max-width: 52ch; }
  .fcta__btns { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .fcta__sub { display: block; margin-top: 22px; font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); }
</style>
